We purchased this to help complete our collection of Pure Flix movies. We enjoyed the movie and will include it in our ministry movie night (we have a ministry license from Pure Flix) in our rural community.
Loved the plot, loved the way it was executed. Good decent family movie with good moral values. Would recommend it to others.

I really enjoyed this movie and would recommend it to others.
It has a good story and a great message.
